            <text>
                <body>
                    <div xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xml:lang="fr" type="original">
<pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-orig-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>

<p xml:id="p.fr.1" n="1">Dimanche soir 5 Mai 89</p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>

<p xml:id="p.fr.2" n="2">Devant m’absenter demains et étant occupé les Mardi, je me mets à votre disposition pour vous accompagner Mercredi à S<hi rend="super">t</hi> Remy.<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> Nous partirions<hi rend="italics"/> par le train de 8 heures 51, si cela vous convient. Ayant déjà vu M. Peyron, il est convenable que je vous accompagne moi-même.<ptr target="#note-t-2"/></p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>

<p xml:id="p.fr.3" n="3">Bien à vous</p>

<p xml:id="p.fr.4" n="4">Salles</p>
<space unit="lines" quantity="1"/></div>

                    <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                        <pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.1" n="1">Sunday evening, 5 May 1889</p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.2" n="2">Having to go away tomorrow and being busy on Tuesdays, I place myself at your disposal to accompany you to St-Rémy on Wednesday.<ptr target="#note-t-1"/> We would leave by the 8.51 train, if that suits you. Having already seen <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_568">Mr Peyron</rs>, it is appropriate that I should accompany you myself.<ptr target="#note-t-2"/></p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
<p xml:id="p.en.3" n="3">Yours truly,</p>
<p xml:id="p.en.4" n="4"><rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_663">Salles</rs></p><space unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                    </div>
                </body>
            </text>
