<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Written on the back of a calling card; the text printed on the front reads:</p><p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" rend="indent">‘Frédéric Salles,</p> <p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" rend="indent">Pasteur de l’Eglise réformée.</p><p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" rend="indent">9, rue de la Rotonde, Arles’.</p>
                                    
                                
